tuelle Rezeption: Margarete Schütte-Lihotzky – ein Mythos der Architekturgeschichte im spannenden Dialog.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 4aArchitekturgeschichte der Moderne. 4aBiografieforschung. 4aGender Studies. 4aMargarete Schütte-Lihotzky. 4aWiderstand gegen den Nationalsozialismus. 4aZeitgeschichte und Kommunismusforschung. 7aARCHITECTURE / Individual Architects & Firms / General.2bisacsh1 aAßmann, Carla, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBast, Gerald, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBaum, David, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBoeckl-Klamper, Elisabeth, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBois, Marcel, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBois, Marcel, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aChang, Helen Young, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDeutsch, Marie-Theres, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDogramaci, Burcu, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEngelmann, Sebastian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFlierl, Thomas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFreyer, Christoph, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGrancy, Antje Senarclens de, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHochhäusl, Sophie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMugrauer, Manfred, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPlakolm-Forsthuber, Sabine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPlatzer, Monika, eco